title: Restore The Array
content:
A program was supposed to print an array of integers. The program forgot to print whitespaces and the array is printed as a string of digits and all we know is that all integers in the array were in the range  and there are no leading zeros in the array.
Given the string  and the integer . There can be multiple ways to restore the array.
Return the number of possible array that can be printed as a string  using the mentioned program.
The number of ways could be very large so return it modulo 
 










 


.
 consists of only digits and doesn't contain leading zeros.
